{"tid":130893,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"現場傳槍聲","createTime":"2017-02-22T16:28:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-22T16:29:30.000Z","uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cc4e968b0dafa91568fc9bb05819ebe679fa2fa4","tid":130893,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T16:28:22.000Z","msg":"和平集會變衝突 現場傳槍聲至少一傷<br />\n[2015.08.10] <br />\n <br />\n黑人青年布朗被白人警員槍殺周年，該市有民眾集會遊行，深夜演變成警民對峙，外電報道現場傳出數十響槍聲，至少一示威者受傷。<br />\n<br />\n周日的遊行一直保持和平，但深夜卻變成騷亂。法新社稱，有一群示威者洗劫商舖，又和全副防暴裝備的警察衝突。法新社記者稱聽到約20響槍聲，目擊一名披血示威者躺在地上。<br />\n<br />\n另據路透社報道，當示威群眾霸佔馬路、癱瘓交通之際，槍聲就響起。(法新社/路透社)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mingpaocanada.com/TOR/htm/News/20150810/ttac3_r.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mingpaocanada.com%2FTOR%2Fhtm%2FNews%2F20150810%2Fttac3_r.htm&d=tO8FO7ZpCqi602%2BiQgdm0Gi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=2d996a4c\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.mingpaocanada.com/TOR/htm/News/20150810/ttac3_r.htm</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28d63e542ae85f8ff6c75ba02849284be8b9e985","tid":130893,"uid":12456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T16:29:30.000Z","msg":"On9"}]}